%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as User / Persona
    participant API as Spring Boot REST API
    participant MCP as MCP Registry/Layer
    participant Jira as Jira Tool (Adapter)
    participant KB as pgvector Knowledge Base
    participant Bedrock as Bedrock Model (LLM)
    participant Risk as Risk Agent
    participant Cost as Cost Agent
    participant Sched as Scheduling Agent

    User->>API: Analyze the following project <br/>tasks and Jira issues to <br/>identify potential risks

    API->>MCP: Request tools for agents

    par Parallel Agent Execution
        API->>Risk: Invoke Risk Agent
        Risk->>MCP: Call Jira Tool
        MCP->>Jira: Fetch Jira issues
        Jira-->>MCP: Return issues
        Risk->>MCP: Call Bedrock Tool
        MCP->>Bedrock: Risk analysis prompt
        Bedrock-->>MCP: Risk results
        MCP-->>Risk: Return risk analysis
        Risk-->>API: Risks

        API->>Cost: Invoke Cost Agent
        Cost->>MCP: Call KB Tool
        MCP->>KB: Query embeddings
        KB-->>MCP: Return similar tasks
        Cost->>MCP: Call Bedrock Tool
        MCP->>Bedrock: Cost optimization prompt
        Bedrock-->>MCP: Cost results
        MCP-->>Cost: Return cost analysis
        Cost-->>API: Cost optimization

        API->>Sched: Invoke Scheduling Agent
        Sched->>MCP: Call Jira Tool
        MCP->>Jira: Fetch Jira issues
        Jira-->>MCP: Return issues
        Sched->>MCP: Call Bedrock Tool
        MCP->>Bedrock: Scheduling prompt
        Bedrock-->>MCP: Schedule results
        MCP-->>Sched: Return schedule analysis
        Sched-->>API: Schedule
    end

    API->>API: Aggregate agent outputs
    API-->>User: Unified AI recommendations (JSON)
